snippet.title: 7 Most Illogical Movie Endings

localized.description:
7 Most Illogical Movie Endings
Subscribe Now! ► http://bit.ly/SubClevverMovies

A great movie can be ruined by a bad ending that just doesn't make sense.  With that in mind, we take a look at 7 films with endings that are so illogical, we can't help but go "huh?"
